Bank Capitalizations ‘Main Course’ in EU Bank Regulator Meeting

-- B y   J i m   B r u n s d e n
-- 
2011-10-04T16:26:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/bank-capitalizations-main-course-in-eu-bank-regulator-meeting.html
Andrea Enria, chairman of the
European Banking Authority, said bank-capitalisaition issues
will be the “main course” at tomorrow’s meeting of the agency.  “We are in a really dangerous interconnection between
sovereigns and the banks,” he said at the European Parliament
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
